(224, 'Nhá»¯ng loáº¡i dÆ°á»¡ng cháº¥t tá»‘t cho ngÆ°Æ¡Ì€i mÄƒÌc bÃªÌ£nh thÃ¢Ìp khÆ¡Ìp', 'Ä‚n uá»‘ng c&acirc;n báº±ng, khoa há»c v&agrave; duy tr&igrave; cuá»™c sá»‘ng hoáº¡t Ä‘á»™ng kh&ocirc;ng chá»‰ tá»‘t cho táº¥t cáº£ má»i ngÆ°á»i m&agrave; c&ograve;n ráº¥t c&oacute; lá»£i cho nh&oacute;m ngÆ°á»i máº¯c bá»‡nh vi&ecirc;m khá»›p. 6 dÆ°á»¡ng cháº¥t dÆ°á»›i Ä‘&acirc;y l&agrave; nh&oacute;m c&aacute;c há»£p cháº¥t ráº¥t há»¯u &iacute;ch cho ngÆ°á»i máº¯c bá»‡nh vi&ecirc;m khá»›p, nháº¥t l&agrave; Ä‘Æ°á»£c bá»• sung qua con Ä‘Æ°á»ng Äƒn uá»‘ng.', NULL, '<p style="color: #166510; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium; color: #000000;">1. Ax&iacute;t b&eacute;o Omega-3</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #166510; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium; color: #000000;">Ax&iacute;t b&eacute;o Omega-3<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>l&agrave; há»£p cháº¥t ráº¥t há»¯u &iacute;ch cho cÆ¡ thá»ƒ, nháº¥t l&agrave; cho c&aacute;c khá»›p gá»‘i, l&agrave; nh&oacute;m má»¡ Ä‘áº·c biá»‡t m&agrave; cÆ¡ thá»ƒ con ngÆ°á»i kh&ocirc;ng sáº£n xuáº¥t Ä‘Æ°á»£c. CÆ¡ thá»ƒ cáº§n Ä‘áº¿n loáº¡i má»¡ n&agrave;y Ä‘á»ƒ táº­p há»£p táº¿ b&agrave;o, táº¡o ra c&aacute;c há»£p cháº¥t dáº¡ng hormon c&oacute; t&ecirc;n l&agr